{"tid":941594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【乘客小心】今次係城巴 座椅遭插針","createTime":"2018-12-15T02:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T05:02:39.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1ab48f666fe4fe06e375244219609bbfcbfdc1","tid":941594,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"再有巴士發現座椅藏針！今晨8時左右，一輛城巴969X由天水圍開往銅鑼灣，至第二站天瑞路時，有乘客告訴車長，指上層左邊第三行近走廊的座位，有一支約4厘米長的針插住。司機查看確定後報警，事件中無人受傷，警方到場調查，列作刑事毀壞案跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181215/59032479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032479&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=08610b1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032479&h=c9c37245\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181215/59032479</a>"},{"pid":"017f53adb8e69af99a6842ad97106ecc71aa220b","tid":941594,"uid":40624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"N賓又開工啦"},{"pid":"e5c942071d2a4307e80ce75c0fb5519ea7fbad1b","tid":941594,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"波台狗又玩野？"},{"pid":"f4130e05720b23275435572eb4ab5ed6679b2788","tid":941594,"uid":170044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"017f53adb8e69af99a6842ad97106ecc71aa220b","tid":941594,"uid":40624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"N賓又開工啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"唔好屈 佢放開觀塘區"},{"pid":"6541359136c9e697185fdb0505dfabc61b706656","tid":941594,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"拉人未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日係度談笑風生"},{"pid":"6b218ba74d9b9f0d82e